@startuml
title REPORT.RF001 - Gerar Boletim Individual

actor "ADMIN / STAFF / STUDENT" as User

boundary Frontend
control ReportResolver
control ReportService
control GPAService
control FrequencyService
control PDFService
control AuditService

database PostgreSQL

User -> Frontend : Solicita boletim individual

Frontend -> ReportResolver : query generateReport(studentId)

ReportResolver -> ReportService : generateReport(studentId)

ReportService -> PostgreSQL : validarPermissão()

alt Permissão concedida

    ReportService -> PostgreSQL : buscarAluno()

    PostgreSQL --> ReportService : dadosAluno

    ReportService -> PostgreSQL : buscarNotas()

    PostgreSQL --> ReportService : notas

    ReportService -> PostgreSQL : buscarFrequencias()

    PostgreSQL --> ReportService : frequências

    ReportService -> GPAService : calcularGPA()

    GPAService --> ReportService : GPA

    ReportService -> FrequencyService : calcularPercentual()

    FrequencyService --> ReportService : percentual

    ReportService -> ReportService : determinarStatus()

    alt GPA >= 7 AND frequência >= 75%

        ReportService -> ReportService : status=APROVADO

    else GPA >=5 AND GPA <7

        ReportService -> ReportService : status=RECUPERAÇÃO

    else

        ReportService -> ReportService : status=REPROVADO

    end

    ReportService -> PDFService : gerarPDF()

    PDFService --> ReportService : boletim.pdf

    ReportService -> AuditService : registrarGeração()

    AuditService --> ReportService : log salvo

    ReportService --> ReportResolver : arquivo PDF

    ReportResolver --> Frontend : download PDF

    Frontend --> User : Boletim gerado

else Sem permissão

    ReportResolver --> Frontend : HTTP 403

    Frontend --> User : Acesso negado

end

@enduml